 This collection of ARexx programmes has been created for the users of
 the game Klondike who wish to create *EASILY* their own card games.
 To operate, you must have :

  - OS 3.0 or better.
  - ARexx.
  - ADPro version 2.5 or better.
  - Sufficient memory (4Meg FAST minimum) and of course a hard disc.
  
 Note : If you do not have the game Klondike Deluxe AGA, Klondike ADPTools
        will not do anything for you !!!
